textBeforeTable: - Cliff http://dissociativeidentityproductions.com/ dissociative.id.productions@gmail.com Why hello hello and welcome to Dissociative Identity here on WKDU Philadelphia, 91.7 fm Sorry for missing last week but due to the circumstances, figure this week should be even better. It's going to be mainly new material so get ready for everything from Norwegian Arms to Clinic, Lamps to Cold War Kids. Should be a mighty swell time. So tune in and enjoy some classic old fashioned radio with your friends here at Dissociative Identity and WKDU. Dissociative Identity on Wed 1/30/13
